<div style="background-color:#b8b8b8; color:white; padding:20px; font-size:22px; line-height:150%;text-align: left;">What is a Guest Certificate and how do I obtain one?</div>
<p style="padding:20px 20px 20px 20px;">A Guest Certificate is issued when a Club Member wishes to allow another person (a non-member) to use their club portfolio. In order to obtain a Guest Certificate, the member needs to contact contact the call centre or send an email to <a href="mailto:correspondence@vrs.co.za" class="purpleLinks">correspondence@vrs.co.za</a> with the following information:</p>
<p style="padding:20px 20px 20px 20px;">1) QVC membership number<br />
2) Reservation number<br />
3) Completed and signed Power of Attorney form<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(can be obtained from the call centre or <a href="documents/VRS-PowerOfAttorneyLetter.pdf" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none; color:#7c046d;">click here</a>)<br />
4) Name and surname of guest<br />
5) Copy of Guest ID document<br />
6) Guest email address<br />
7) Guest telephone number<br /></p>

<p style="padding:20px 20px 20px 20px;">It is the guests' responsibility to confirm the reservation with the resort and to present proof of identification when checking in.</p>

<div style="background-color:#b8b8b8; color:white; padding:20px; font-size:22px; line-height:150%;text-align: left;">I received a Buyer's Award midweek or weekend gift certificate while attending a seminar. How can I make a booking with the voucher that I received?</div>

<p style="padding:20px 20px 20px 20px;">If you have a One Year Gift voucher you will need to go to <a class="purpleLinks" href="http://www.oneyeargift.co.za/home.seam" target="_blank">www.oneyeargift.co.za</a> and follow the registration process to redeem your voucher, for further queries click "contact us and a consultant will be able to assist you shortly"</p>

